<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-08-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-08-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="144" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d144">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Chile</gloss> to
                                President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi></placeName>, <hi rend="italic"><date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-08-23">August 23,
                                        1906</date>.</hi></dateline></opener>
                        <p>The heartfelt expressions of condolence which you have deigned to
                            reiterate have touched the Chilean heart in a grateful and profound
                            manner. It will never forget that in this hour of ordeal it had at its
                            side the great nation you so nobly represent.</p>
                        <p>Again I thank you most cordially.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Jerman Riesco.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>